00:29:46,117 --> 00:29:47,786
PAIK MIN-JAE, THE WINNER OF
INTERNATIONAL MATHEMATICAL CONTEST…

382
00:30:08,306 --> 00:30:14,312
WHAT'S THE PROBABILITY WHEN "N" POINTS…

